OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,FHayat Ghalayini told ITV News' Rachel
OL,7,FTownsend she is 'living without a
OL,8,Fsoul' as her daughters remain trapped
OL,9,Fin Gaza
OL,11,F"I am living, but without a soul" is
OL,12,Fhow Hayat Alghanayini describes her
OL,13,Flife now.
OL,15,FBy some, she will be considered one of
OL,16,Fthe lucky ones, evacuated from Gaza in
OL,17,Fthe weeks after the October 7 attacks.
OL,18,FBut it meant leaving her four
OL,19,Fdaughters behind, and for Hayat, the
OL,20,Fburden of separation is unbearable.
