OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,F"This was the beginning of the journey
OL,7,Fof pain," she tells us.
OL,9,FITV News finds her youngest daughter,
OL,10,FDanya, having evacuated Gaza City
OL,11,Fafter their family home was bombed.
OL,13,FWe ask her what it would mean to see
OL,14,Fher mother again: "All I can think
OL,15,Fabout is hugging my mother. Touching
OL,16,Fher and being with her. That is all I
OL,17,Fcan think about."
