OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,FDanya was living with her three
OL,7,Fsisters, their mother and their
OL,8,Fstepfather, who has four children of
OL,9,Fhis own.
OL,11,FHe is a British citizen and was
OL,12,Foffered safety in the UK. As the main
OL,13,Fcarer for his four children, Hayat
OL,14,Ffaced an almost impossible choice:
OL,15,Fflee to safety or stay in war-torn
OL,16,FGaza with her daughters.
