OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,FThinking it would be just for a matter
OL,7,Fof weeks and encouraged by her four
OL,8,Fdaughters, Hayat reluctantly came to
OL,9,FManchester in December 2023. She has
OL,10,Fnot seen her daughters for almost two
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"I have to leave part of my family in
OL,14,FGaza, and another part will go out. I
OL,15,Ffeel that my life has stopped now.
OL,16,FThat is when the pain and the guilt
OL,17,Fstarted. I don't sleep because of the
OL,18,Fguilt, and when I do simple things
OL,19,Flike eating, all I feel is guilt."
