OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,FAnd then the family were given hope,
OL,7,Fwhen Hayat's youngest daughter Danya
OL,8,Fwas granted a scholarship at a school
OL,9,Fin Berkshire. But with no visa, hope
OL,10,Fis dissipating.
OL,12,F"Students like me dream," Danya told
OL,13,FITV News.
OL,15,F"Despite what everyone has been
OL,16,Fthrough, we still want to study. The
OL,17,Fschools and the universities have all
OL,18,Fbeen bombed, so there is no way of
OL,19,Fstudying here."
