OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,FWe put their story to the Foreign,
OL,7,FCommonwealth and Development Office,
OL,8,Fwho told us: "We are working at pace
OL,9,Fto assist eligible groups to leave
OL,10,FGaza and come to the UK", but added, "
OL,11,FOur guidance has consistently made
OL,12,Fclear that students must be 18 years
OL,13,For over to be eligible for support."
OL,15,FHayat describes a happy, perfect
OL,16,Ffamily life. They had just celebrated
OL,17,Ftheir daughter's 14th birthday. Little
OL,18,Fdid they know it would be the last
OL,19,Fthey would celebrate together
