OL,3,C'Living without a soul': Mother
OL,4,Cseparated from daughters in Gaza
OL,6,FDanya said: "Right now, I feel like
OL,7,FI'm in a prison, in a jar where I can
OL,8,Fsee the outside world but can't do
OL,9,Fanything."
OL,11,FHayat added: "I don't want anything
OL,12,Felse from life. I just want them to be
OL,13,Fwith me again. I am praying every day.
OL,14,FI've tried everything I can but
OL,15,Fthere's nothing."
